.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LIQUIDITY-ADS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-liquidity-ads \- list nodes advertising liquidity via option_will_fund
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-liquidity-ads
.SH DESCRIPTION
Scans the local gossip graph for nodes that advertise the
.B option_will_fund
field (liquidity ads per BOLT-12 extension).
Returns an empty array if no nodes advertise liquidity or the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{nodeid, alias, option_will_fund:{...}}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-gossip (1),
.BR lightning-channel-open (1)
